---
// Pull: typographic pull quote, breaks out of prose flow as editorial emphasis
---

<aside class="pull">
  <slot />
</aside>

<style>
  .pull {
    margin: 2.5em 0;
    padding: 0.65em 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--accent-dim);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--accent-dim);
    font-family: 'EB Garamond', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 1.45rem;
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.35;
    color: var(--accent);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
</style>
